BODY.HEAD:
The Knave in Graine;
OR
New Vampt.

SP.P:
And if you please, let it goe to the Punkes delight;
'tis your onely sweet tune: for women doe love the Punks
delight.

What, my fretfull Doctour? the only curer of mad
folks;


Know I my selfe?

To the Society at the Swan two pottles and a halfe:
Monkey the health; these are my noble & prime visi tants;
the boxes I gave you to lay up.
